Reviewed-by: Pierre Gondois <pierre.gondois@arm.com>
Reviewed-by: Lifeng Zheng <zhenglifeng1@huawei.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20260206142658.72583-7-sumitg@nvidia.com
